---
interface Props {
  part?: 1 | 2;
  side?: 'left' | 'right';
  pageNumber?: number;
}

const { part = 1, side = 'right', pageNumber } = Astro.props;
---
<div class="magazine-page h-full">
  <div class="page-content h-full flex flex-col relative">
    {part === 1 && (
      <>
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-primary mb-1">Création de site web</h2>
          <p class="text-sm font-poppins italic text-dark/60 leading-relaxed">
            Un site doux, clair et aligné, pensé pour révéler ton univers.
          </p>
          <div class="h-1 w-12 bg-primary/40 mt-2"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-8 flex-grow flex flex-col justify-center">
          <!-- Introduction -->
          <p class="text-[14px] font-sans leading-relaxed text-dark/80 max-w-prose">
            Je crée des sites web sensibles, élégants et intuitifs, qui respirent ton énergie et accompagnent ton activité avec douceur. Chaque site est pensé comme une expérience : simple, fluide, lumineuse, et profondément alignée avec qui tu es.
          </p>

          <!-- Ce que tu reçois -->
          <div class="p-8 rounded-[2.5rem] bg-highlight/30 border border-highlight relative overflow-hidden w-full">
            <div class="absolute top-6 right-6 text-highlight/60">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-sparkles"><path d="m12 3-1.912 5.813a2 2 0 0 1-1.275 1.275L3 12l5.813 1.912a2 2 0 0 1 1.275 1.275L12 21l1.912-5.813a2 2 0 0 1 1.275-1.275L21 12l-5.813-1.912a2 2 0 0 1-1.275-1.275L12 3Z"/><path d="M5 3v4"/><path d="M19 17v4"/><path d="M3 5h4"/><path d="M17 19h4"/></svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-dark mb-6">Ce que tu reçois</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-[13px] font-sans text-dark/80">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-primary bg-white/80 shrink-0 mt-0.5 shadow-sm">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
                </div>
                <span>Arborescence claire et intuitive</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-primary bg-white/80 shrink-0 mt-0.5 shadow-sm">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
                </div>
                <span>Design sur-mesure, poétique et professionnel</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-primary bg-white/80 shrink-0 mt-0.5 shadow-sm">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
                </div>
                <span>Pages essentielles (Accueil, À propos, Services, Contact)</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-primary bg-white/80 shrink-0 mt-0.5 shadow-sm">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
                </div>
                <span>Intégration de ton identité visuelle</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-primary bg-white/80 shrink-0 mt-0.5 shadow-sm">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
                </div>
                <span>Textes optimisés</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-primary bg-white/80 shrink-0 mt-0.5 shadow-sm">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
                </div>
                <span>Version mobile responsive</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-primary bg-white/80 shrink-0 mt-0.5 shadow-sm">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
                </div>
                <span>Installation + mise en ligne</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-primary bg-white/80 shrink-0 mt-0.5 shadow-sm">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-check"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
                </div>
                <span>Guide d’utilisation pour être autonome</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </>
    )}

    {part === 2 && (
      <div class="flex flex-col justify-center flex-grow space-y-8">
        <!-- Le processus -->
        <div class="p-8 rounded-[2.5rem] bg-accent/10 border border-accent/20 relative overflow-hidden w-full">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-dark mb-6">Le processus</h3>
          <ol class="space-y-3 text-[13px] font-sans text-dark/80">
            <li class="flex gap-4">
              <span class="font-bold text-accent">1.</span>
              <span>Appel ou questionnaire pour comprendre ton univers</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-4">
              <span class="font-bold text-accent">2.</span>
              <span>Proposition d’ambiance et structure du site</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-4">
              <span class="font-bold text-accent">3.</span>
              <span>Création du design complet</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-4">
              <span class="font-bold text-accent">4.</span>
              <span>Intégration des contenus</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-4">
              <span class="font-bold text-accent">5.</span>
              <span>Ajustements et finalisation</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-4">
              <span class="font-bold text-accent">6.</span>
              <span>Mise en ligne + guide d’autonomie</span>
            </li>
          </ol>
        </div>

        <!-- Pour qui ? -->
        <div class="relative px-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-dark mb-3">Pour qui ?</h3>
          <p class="text-[13px] font-sans leading-relaxed text-dark/80 italic">
            Pour les indépendantes, TPE et PME qui recherchent un site web fiable, esthétique et facile à gérer, conçu pour soutenir leur croissance et renforcer leur présence en ligne.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Tarifs -->
        <div class="p-8 rounded-[2.5rem] bg-primary/10 border border-primary/20 relative overflow-hidden">
          <div class="absolute top-6 right-6 text-primary/30">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-sun"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="4"/><path d="M12 2v2"/><path d="M12 20v2"/><path d="m4.93 4.93 1.41 1.41"/><path d="m17.66 17.66 1.41 1.41"/><path d="M2 12h2"/><path d="M20 12h2"/><path d="m6.34 17.66-1.41 1.41"/><path d="m19.07 4.93-1.41 1.41"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-dark mb-2">Tarif</h3>
          <p class="text-[14px] font-sans text-dark/80">
            Le tarif est défini sur devis, selon la structure du site, le nombre de pages et les fonctionnalités nécessaires à ton activité.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- CTA -->
        <div class="pt-6 text-center">
          <p class="text-base font-poppins italic text-dark/60 mb-6">
            Prête à donner vie à ton univers en ligne ?
          </p>
          <button class="px-12 py-4 rounded-full bg-primary text-white font-sans font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-primary/90 transition-all shadow-xl shadow-primary/20 transform hover:-translate-y-1">
            Créer mon site
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    )}
    {pageNumber && (
      <div class={`absolute bottom-4 ${side === 'left' ? 'left-4' : 'right-4'} text-[10px] font-serif text-black italic`}>
        {pageNumber}
      </div>
    )}
  </div>
  <!-- Page Navigation Buttons -->
  {side === 'left' && (
    <button class="st-ignore btn-prev-page absolute left-2 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-highlight shadow-lg border-2 border-accent flex items-center justify-center text-accent hover:bg-accent hover:text-highlight transition-all z-50">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m15 18-6-6 6-6"/></svg>
    </button>
  )}
  {side === 'right' && (
    <button class="st-ignore btn-next-page absolute right-2 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-highlight shadow-lg border-2 border-accent flex items-center justify-center text-accent hover:bg-accent hover:text-highlight transition-all z-50">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m9 18 6-6-6-6"/></svg>
    </button>
  )}
</div>
